sues. The book would later see two brief revivals before it ended; the first was in 1951 when Fawcett briefly resurrected the series for five more issues, the second came in 1955 when Charlton printed reprints of the series but this only lasted for four issues and after that the title's compiled numbering was continued in the Charlton series, <a href=\\\"\\/fightin-navy\\/4050-36532\\/\\\" data-ref-id=\\\"4050-36532\\\">Fightin' Navy<\\/a>.<\\/p><h4>Publishers<\\/h4><ul><li>#01-69: <a href=\\\"\\/fawcett-publications\\/4010-34\\/\\\" data-ref-id=\\\"4010-34\\\">Fawcett Publications<\\/a><\\/li><li>#70-73: <a href=\\\"\\/charlton\\/4010-125\\/\\\" data-ref-id=\\\"4010-125\\\">Charlton<\\/a><\\/li><\\/ul><h4>Collected Edition<\\/h4><ul><li><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/comicvine.gamespot.com\\/gwandanaland-comics-1272-the-complete-singapore-sa\\/4000-680834\\/\\\">The Complete Singapore Sal<\\/a> (SS stories from #47, 51, 57 and 60)<\\/li><\\/ul><p> <\\/p>\",\"first_issue\":{\"api_detail_url\":\"https:\\/\\/comicvine.gamespot.com\\/api\\/issue\\/4000-92218\\/\",\"id\":92218,\"name\":null,\"issue_number\":\"1\"},\"id\":978,\"image\":{\"icon_url\":\"https:\\/\\/comicvine.gamespot.com\\/api\\/image\\/square_avatar\\/59223-978-92218-1-don-winslow-of-the-n.jpg\",\"medium_url\":\"https:\\/\\/comicvine.gamespot.com\\/api\\/image\\/scale_medium\\/59223-978-92218-1-don-winslow-of-the-n.jpg\",\"screen_url\":\"https:\\/\\/comicvine.gamespot.com\\/api\\/image\\/screen_medium\\/59223-978-92218-1-don-winslow-of-the-n.jpg\",\"screen_large_url\":\"https:\\/\\/comicvine.gamespot.com\\/api\\/image\\/screen_kubrick\\/59223-978-92218-1-don-winslow-of-the-n.jpg\",\"small_url\":\"https:\\/\\/comicvine.gamespot.com\\/api\\/image\\/scale_small\\/59223-978-92218-1-don-winslow-of-the-n.jpg\",\"super_url\":\"https:\\/\\/comicvine.gamespot.com\\/api\\/image\\/scale_large\\/59223-978-92218-1-don-winslow-of-the-n.jpg\",\"thumb_url\":\"https:\\/\\/comicvine.gamespot.com\\/api\\/image\\/scale_avatar\\/592