itles reflected the fact that competitor Archie Comics had turned teen comics into big business through its popular freckle faced hero.<\\/p>\",\"first_issue\":{\"api_detail_url\":\"https:\\/\\/comicvine.gamespot.com\\/api\\/issue\\/4000-56353\\/\",\"id\":56353,\"name\":null,\"issue_number\":\"1\"},\"id\":1168,\"image\":{\"icon_url\":\"https:\\/\\/comicvine.gamespot.com\\/api\\/image\\/square_avatar\\/47008-1168-56353-1-leave-it-to-binky.jpg\",\"medium_url\":\"https:\\/\\/comicvine.gamespot.com\\/api\\/image\\/scale_medium\\/47008-1168-56353-1-leave-it-to-binky.jpg\",\"screen_url\":\"https:\\/\\/comicvine.gamespot.com\\/api\\/image\\/screen_medium\\/47008-1168-56353-1-leave-it-to-binky.jpg\",\"screen_large_url\":\"https:\\/\\/comicvine.gamespot.com\\/api\\/image\\/screen_kubrick\\/47008-1168-56353-1-leave-it-to-binky.jpg\",\"small_url\":\"https:\\/\\/comicvine.gamespot.com\\/api\\/image\\/scale_small\\/47008-1168-56353-1-leave-it-to-binky.jpg\",\"super_url\":\"https:\\/\\/comicvine.gamespot.com\\/api\\/image\\/scale_large\\/47008-1168-56353-1-leave-it-to-binky.jpg\",\"thumb_url\":\"https:\\/\\/comicvine.gamespot.com\\/api\\/image\\/scale_avatar\\/47008-1168-56353-1-leave-it-to-binky.jpg\",\"tiny_url\":\"https:\\/\\/comicvine.gamespot.com\\/api\\/image\\/square_mini\\/47008-1168-56353-1-leave-it-to-binky.jpg\",\"original_url\":\"https:\\/\\/comicvine.gamespot.com\\/api\\/image\\/original\\/47008-1168-56353-1-leave-it-to-binky.jpg\",\"image_tags\":\"All Images\"},\"last_issue\":{\"api_detail_url\":\"https:\\/\\/comicvine.gamespot.com\\/api\\/issue\\/4000-56412\\/\",\"id\":56412,\"name\":null,\"issue_number\":\"60\"},\"name\":\"Leave it to Binky\",\"publisher\":{\"api_detail_url\":\"https:\\/\\/comicvine.gamespot.com\\/api\\/publisher\\/4010-10\\/\",\"id\":10,\"name\":\"DC Comics\"},\"site_detail_url\":\"https:\\/\\/comicvine.gamespot.com\\/leave-it-to-binky\\/4050-1168\\/\",\"start_year\":\"1948\"},{\"aliases\":null,\"api_detail_url\":\"https:\\/\\/comicvine.gamespot.